<footer class="grow p-5 z-5  md:mx-auto md:py-5 lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-xl">
    <p>Made with love <span class="inline-block animate-bounce">❤️</span> using super experimental technologies like <a class="transition-all duration-150 hover:ring hover:ring-offset-1 hover:ring-on-background" href="{{tools.deno.url}}" target="_blank">{{tools.deno.title}}</a> & <a class="transition-all duration-150 hover:ring hover:ring-offset-1 hover:ring-on-background" href="{{tools.lume.url}}" target="_blank">{{tools.lume.title}}</a>
